status: MARC21-007: Color of the image for microforms
Color of the image for microforms.

scope note (en): Includes only one color or hue other than black, for example, blue-and-white (blue-and-transparent). Always used for microopaques.

definition (en): Combination of one-color and multicolored images.
Color of the microform is not known.
Color other than black-and-white, multicolored, mixed.
